## Features Implemented (All from PRD)

### ✅ Core Payment (Section 4)
- Mock OTP login
- Send money via UPI ID or phone
- **QR Code Scanner** — dual mode: camera scan + image upload (works on both emulator and device)
- Receive money (QR display)
- Transaction history with risk tags

### ✅ SMS Fraud Detection (Section 5.1)
- **On-device** (local): Keyword detection across 8 categories (urgency, KYC scam, money request, prize scam, phishing, impersonation, OTP scam, financial threat)
- **Cloud** (Flask): Deep rule-based analysis with URL detection, grammar analysis, capitalization detection
- SMS inbox view + manual input + 4 quick templates
- Risk score (0–100) + classification (safe/suspicious/high_risk)

### ✅ Transaction Intention Scorer (Section 5.2)
- **4-category weighted scoring**:
  - User Profile (25%): amount deviation, unusual time, absolute amount
  - Recipient Profile (30%): new vs existing, merchant vs individual, trust score
  - Relationship Profile (20%): transaction count, usual amount range
  - Context (25%): QR trigger, link trigger, SMS flag, call state, sudden navigation
- Score ranges → interventions (exactly as PRD):
  - 0–50: No warning
  - 50–80: Soft warning popup
  - 80–95: Strong warning + checkbox required
  - 95+: 10-second delay + checkbox

### ✅ Call-Aware Risk Boost (Section 5.3)
- Demo toggle on home screen to simulate active call
- Unknown caller toggle for higher boost
- Only call state (no audio) — privacy safe

### ✅ Risk Interventions (Section 5.1 User Intervention)
- **Medium Risk**: Warning popup with risk factors
- **High Risk**: Strong warning + checkbox "I understand the risks and still want to proceed"
- **Critical Risk**: Full-screen dark alert + 10-second animated countdown + cancel option during delay

### ✅ Explanation System
- Risk factor breakdown with bar chart (FL Chart)
- Highlighted SMS text (risky words in red/orange)
- Expert analysis with advice (from /explain-risk API)
- Contribution scores per factor

---

## Backend Testing Results

```
SMS Analysis Test:
  Input: "URGENT: Your bank account BLOCKED due to KYC. Update at http://fake-bank.xyz/kyc"
  Result: Score 86, Classification: high_risk, 4 risk factor categories detected

API Endpoints:
  ✅ POST /analyze-sms — Returns risk score, highlighted words, factor breakdown
  ✅ POST /risk-score — Returns weighted score, intervention level, factors
  ✅ POST /explain-risk — Returns narrative, detailed explanations, advice
```

