## Next Steps (After Flutter Setup)

1. Install Flutter SDK → see [SETUP_INSTRUCTIONS.md](file:///c:/Users/Kavy%20Khilrani/Desktop/Projects/Wallupi/SETUP_INSTRUCTIONS.md)
2. Run `flutter pub get` in the `frontend/` directory
3. Start backend: `python app.py` in `backend/`
4. Run app: `flutter run` in `frontend/`
5. Test all 3 flows (normal → fraud warning → critical delay)
